### ============================================================================
### ADMIN → COMPANIES — /api/v1/admin/companies
### ============================================================================

### List companies
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/companies
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get company by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/companies/{{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Create company
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/companies
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Acme Corp",
  "industry": "Healthcare",
  "totalCredits": 1000,
  "billing_currency": "NGN"
}

### Get company employees
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/companies/{{companyId}}/employees
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Update company
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/companies/{{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Acme Corp Updated",
  "industry": "Pharmaceuticals"
}

### Freeze company
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/companies/{{companyId}}/freeze
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Unfreeze company
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/companies/{{companyId}}/unfreeze
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Add credits to company
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/companies/{{companyId}}/add-credits
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 500
}

### Upgrade company tier
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/companies/{{companyId}}/upgrade-tier
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Delete company
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/companies/{{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
